40 Wandering Spirit 4 The Pokémon exchanges Abilities with a Pokémon that hits it with a contact move.

Disc Ability Score Description

Disc 17 Mimicry 3 Changes the Pokémon's type depending on the terrain.
Disc 20 Rock Head 6 Protects the Pokémon from recoil damage.
Disc 21 Poison Heal 8 Restores HP if the Pokémon is poisoned instead of losing HP.
Disc 22 Shadow Tag 10 This Pokémon steps on the opposing Pokémon's shadow to prevent it from escaping.

Disc 34 Liquid Ooze 3 The oozed liquid has a strong stench, which damages attackers using draining moves.
Disc 48 Oblivious 3 The Pokémon is oblivious, and that keeps it from being infatuated or taunted.
